items.name: Cold Case Wiki
items.title: Cold Case Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Cold Case Wiki
items.desc: Cold Case Wiki is a collaborative database about the hit CBS TV series "Cold Case" which premiered in 2003. Here, you'll find information on episodes, characters, actors, writers, directors, and all other things "Cold Case." If you want to share your "Cold Case" knowledge with your fellow fans, join us today. This is a community site that anyone can edit, including you!

items.name: Cold Case Wiki
items.title: Cold Case Wiki
items.headline: Willkommen bei dem Cold Case Wiki
items.desc:
Dieses Wiki behandelt die leider abgesetzte Crime Drama Serie Cold Case, eine Squad, die ungelöste Fälle löst. 
Die Cold Case Squad beseht aus der Hauptcharakter Lilly Rush, John Stillman, Nick Vera und Will Jeffries. Ergänzt wird die Squad mit Scotty Valens und Kat Miller.

Die Serie wurde für den Primetime Emmy norminiert. Die erste Folge wurde von CBS in der USA am 9. Juni 2004 ausgestrahlt, in Deutschland übernahm Kabel 1 die Ausstrahlung.

items.name: Wiki Criminal Case
items.title: Wiki Criminal Case
items.headline: Bienvenido a la wiki Criminal Case
items.desc: Este es un wiki en el que puedes resolver crímenes. Revisamos cada caso en detalle. Si usted está teniendo problemas para resolver una escena o un puzzle, simplemente dejar un mensaje a continuación y le responderemos de inmediato. Se encuentra en la miniatura de cada escena del crimen, que está vinculada a una imagen más grande de ella para que pueda tomar el tiempo para entender y memorizar dónde están todos los objetos ocultos.

items.headline: Welcome To Case Closed Wiki!
items.desc: At Case Closed Wiki, you can find out all the information about Case Closed. You can even read the latest manga for free! We provide fantastic descriptions and summaries. Our theme is magnificent with Conan at the back shooting a Sleeping Dart. Although it is not done, we would appreciate very much if everyone gathers together their knowledge and help us improve things that have stubs and even give suggestions that would benefit this wiki a lot. Thank You!
